### 媒体流
后台
```
const rs = fs.createReadStream('1.avi');
sock.on('video_stream_req', () {
  rs.on('data', (data) => {
    sock.emait('data', data)
  })
})
```

前台
```
sock.emit('video_stream_req');
const m = new MediaSource();
sock.on('data', (buffer) => {
  m.append(buffer);
  sock.emit('video_stream_req');
})
oV.src = URL.createObjectURL(m);
```

